# Project-specific Cursor Rules

## Project Context
This is a Next.js AI chatbot application with streaming LLM responses and weather integration.

## Key Requirements
- Use TypeScript for all code
- Follow Next.js App Router patterns
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Implement streaming responses with OpenAI
- Integrate weather API functionality
- Support message editing

## Code Standards
- Use 'use client' directive for client components
- Keep components modular and focused
- Use TypeScript interfaces for all data structures
- Follow React best practices (hooks, state management)
- Handle errors gracefully with user-friendly messages

## API Routes
- Use Edge Runtime for performance
- Implement proper error handling
- Stream responses for better UX
- Secure API keys server-side only

